title: S12 Ep174: Contact With Non-Human Intelligence
itunes:title: Contact With Non-Human Intelligence
description:
Mary Rodwell was the subject of a charming documentary and showed strength, passion & dedication to her work helping people that have had Alien Abductions & UFO sightings.

Mary has researched more than 3000 cases and suggests extraterrestrial encounters are a global phenomenon. During her visit she shares some of the more unusual accounts she has heard and investigated and her new work with Star Children.
